search_results.title: Alias Mr C: Home
search_results.snippet: You have reached the secret lair of Mr. C. Alas, he is not here. Feel free to browse in his absence, but be forewarned that most things in here have teeth.

search_results.title: Who is this guy?
search_results.snippet: Christopher Jones (alias Mr. C, alias Brother C) has for several years taught classes on history, civics, speech and logic both on- and off-line.
